Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE UNLIKELY SAVIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Dai actually pulled it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance to heal up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of a Behoma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Legends say a phoenix is resurrected\Nfrom its ashes, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was more than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragonic Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrifying ability\Nin both attack and defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot win bare-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I must use my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious legendary weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavens are trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban is going to wield\Nthe most terrible weapon at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my weapon, Kōmanotue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kōmanotue?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcome is decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we both wield weapons\Nmade by Ron Berku,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,our individual strength\Nwill decide this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku made it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The man is a Darkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering how difficult he can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that he gave you humans weapons\Nis the more unlikely scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, I presented him with several\Nweapons, like the Dark Armour Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban chose\Nthe Kōmanotue as his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of weapon is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of a Somatic Staff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It converts Magic Power\Ninto its equivalent in attack power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It functions on the same principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, whereas a Somatic Staff is limited\Nin how much Magic Power it can convert,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kōmanotue suffers\Nno such limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When Dark King Ban wields it\Nwith his tremendous Magic Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes the greatest and\Nmost terribly destructive weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now observe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,his greatest masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink! My Magic Power is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... try it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It broke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The invincible Sword of Dai,\Nmade from Orichalcum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost your will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly anyone has ever\Nfought me this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be proud...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! What's wrong?! Get up! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! You have to get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you like this\Nbefore I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last thing you will ever see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Calamity Wall!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel it for yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel! Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with me on this, Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! My life already belongs\Nto Dai and his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where we are doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to die,\Nwe'd like to die here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,protecting you for one more second,\None more moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let us choose where we die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile. Futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once let loose,\Nno one can stop the Calamity Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you hold my hand\Nuntil the very last moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He rescued us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just that you still live,\Nbut that you sided with the Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't sided with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't want anyone else\Nto kill Dai and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dai had perished...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it would have made my transformation\Ninto a monster meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would have no reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then fear not. For your death is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Core has already\Nfused with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's been removed,\Nyou don't have long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the primary reason you will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I am going\Nto execute you here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have been generous, giving you\Nchance after chance over the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not so forgiving as to smile\Nwhen my prey is stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you need not worry about\Na reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra's presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are King Ban and Lord Hadorra...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We must help Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move and I pierce your Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those four...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here, Mystban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra rescued Dai and his friends\Nfrom King Ban and let them escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, he is going to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness the end of your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! Is everything going to end here?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without fighting the Disciples of Aban?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right here?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not be killed by you twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to take my life so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have no choice\Nbut to defeat you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me, Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:54.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}KAISER PHOENIX{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He repelled my attack?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gave him a body that would grow more\Npowerful each time he was resurrected.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he couldn't be resurrected\Nwithout my Dark Aura.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that he has become a Superior Being,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I assumed that this power was lost!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he brought himself back\Nfrom the brink of death.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now it seems he may actually\Nbe becoming strong enough to rival me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you care\Nwhat happens to your servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die, they die as well anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hadorra Royal Guard stands united!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our sole objective is to defeat\Nthe Disciples of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,None of my servants fear death\Nif it serves our purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was well said, Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban! You're the one dying today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can defeat me\Nwith a meager power increase?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were just that,\NI doubt I could defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in your current condition,\Nit's another story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume that staff absorbs Magic Power\Nand converts it into attack power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, simply holding it\Ndrains your Magic Power continuously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could break the Sword of Dai,\Nbut not this Orichalcum blade...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see now!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting Dai and his friends\Ndrained my Magic Power!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've caught on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,With your Magic Power waning,\Nin a clash of might, I have the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what we'll do\Nif you release these bindings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can assume that the instant you move,\Nyou'll be burned to a crisp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Arrogant little doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, this would reduce me to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your Magic Power\Nreally is weakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't miss this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Ultra Combustion Slash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare ignore your debt\Nfor being made into a Superior Being?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell immobilizes me,\Nbut binds you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That little parasite!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold him right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the tables have turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Block?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after... Lord Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N"Look after Lord Hadorra"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How can those be your first words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Block...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So they've escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew that rook had such an ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A rook...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A castling maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Castling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the game of chess,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a move where\Nthe king and rook can be rearranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That warrior was born from a rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise that\Nthis piece would possess such an ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was just about to finish Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were a game of chess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,castling after a check is cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?! Where's Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he fell with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he still be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what Hyunckel talked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Mother Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. So that's what is said to appear\Nwhen a Dragon Knight's life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai isn't dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai would never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Their weapons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They returned not to their masters,\Nbut to Sir Ron Berku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Dai and the others...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone else will come\Nto try to thwart my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Mother Dragon\Ngives birth to a new Dragon Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it will take decades\Nbefore it is fully grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, it will take less than ten days\Nfor me to reduce the Surface World to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We only need to be careful of\Nany desperate resistance from Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, my subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to bring ruin to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Defeated by Dark King Ban,\Nour heroes escape thanks to Hadorra,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but are all separated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai is suddenly taken away\Nby the Mother Dragon,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while Popp and Maam\Nwash up in Carl Kingdom.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Popp prays for his friends' safety,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.51,0:23:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he learns that Ban has begun\Nhis attack on the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Survivors"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
